Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello, thank you for your interest in the SynchroLife bounty! Yes, we still have about 10 spots avaliable for the blog bounty!  You can post on your own blog, or on a blog site like Medium or Steemit.  Here are some more details for your reference:  Blog and Website Article Post Bounty * Accepting up to 30 articles  Bounty: 450 SynchroCoin (SYC) for one blog post or article  Requirements: - Must an original and unique blog post or article introducing the SynchroLife service and crowdsale. Copy pasting (for example, copy and pasting from our press release, white paper, website, Bitcointalk announcement, other news sites, etc) the entire article will not be accepted. If the SynchroLife team believes your post lacks originality we may ask you to rewrite it. - Blog or article post may be in any language. - Must be 500 words in English (or rough equivalent in your language) - Blog must contain at least one link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (http://synchrolife.org) and to the iOS App Store (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449) and Google Play (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife) pages for SynchroLife. - All images or other content used in the article must be copyright free or owned by you. We can provide any images of SynchroLife as needed including screenshots, images from the website, images from the white paper, and food/restaurant images if needed. You can start with the images here: https://www.dropbox.com/sh/r0j2xfca95q01d7/AAA_MXa1mNlIEXgx3oxin1gsa?dl=0 - Websites and blogs related to cryptocurrency, technology, startups, mobile apps, or food are preferred. - Articles will be approved in the order they are received, up to a maximum of 50 articles.  How to Apply: 1. Write your article and post it on your blog or website 2. Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]

All SynchroCoin (SYC) tokens for bounty will be distributed after the end of the crowdsale (as stated since the beginning of the first round of the bounty). You can follow our project updates on our social media (https://twitter.com/synchrocoin, https://facebook.com/synchrocoin, https://medium.com/@synchrocoin, https://synchrolife-slackin.herokuapp.com/) or download our currently live mobile apps for iOS and Android with over 100,000 downloads and 30,000 active users (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449?mt=8 and https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife).  Please let us know if you have any specific questions regarding the bounty and we will be happy to answer as soon as possible!

Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello! We have just announced the second round of bounty today, including Facebook and Twitter bounty. I will post the information and links here in my response for your convenience!  Let us know if you have any other questions about the Facebook and Twitter bounty.    Daily Twitter and Facebook Bounty  Bounty: 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Twitter (1 stake per day per Twitter post) 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Facebook (1 stake per day per Facebook post)  Requirements: - Share or retweet a post from an official SynchroLife account (Facebook “SynchroCoin”, Twitter “@synchrocoin”) or make an original post which includes a link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) or our Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin. Please note that if your post is private, friends only, or locked we may not be able to verify it. - You must leave the share/retweet/post up until at least the end of the bounty campaign period (October 20, 2017). If the share is no longer avaliable when we check it will not be counted. - Only ONE Facebook post and ONE Twitter post per user per day. Attempts to make multiple accounts or count posts in one day for the whole month will be disqualified and immediately blacklisted from all bounties when discovered. - Twitter accounts must have more than 50 followers. Facebook accounts must have more than 50 friends. - You must follow our official Twitter account to be counted for the Twitter bounty. Similarly, you must like the official Facebook page to be counted for the Facebook bounty.  Please note this is a daily bounty. This means once a day. 😊  🐦 How to Apply for Twitter:  1. Follow SynchroLife on Twitter (@synchrocoin, http://www.twitter.com/synchrocoin) 2. Retweet a Tweet by the official account OR make your own original Tweet that links to the official crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) OR make your own original Tweet that links to our official Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin) 3. Once you have tweeted, fill out this form to apply for the bounty: https://goo.gl/forms/XDaH27cRUuON0ahA3 You can apply for the Twitter bounty once a day. You can fill out the Google Form daily, weekly, or all at the end of the campaign, however is easiest for you. Please note the Google Form requires you to link to the Tweets that you retweeted or to your original Tweets so they can be counted. See the details of the form here: https://goo.gl/forms/XDaH27cRUuON0ahA3  All participants will get 1 stake per retweet or original tweet, up to once a day.  👤 How to Apply for Facebook:  1. Like the official SynchroLife crowdsale Facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/synchrocoin)Post a link to the SynchroLife token crowdsale website (http://synchrolife.org) on your Facebook account 2. Share a Facebook post by the official account OR make your own original Facebook post that links to the official crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) OR make your own original Facebook post that links to our official Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin) 3. Once you have shared or posted, fill out this form to apply for the bounty: https://goo.gl/forms/w9OlxfI63A2WBqbY2 You can apply for the Facebook bounty once a day. You can fill out the Google Form daily, weekly, or all at the end of the campaign, however is easiest for you. Please note the Google Form requires you to link to the Facebook posts that you shared or to your original Facebook posts so they can be counted. See the details of the form here: https://goo.gl/forms/w9OlxfI63A2WBqbY2  All participants will get 1 stake per Facebook post share or original Facebook post, up to once a day.

Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: SYNCHROLIFE BOUNTY CAMPAIGN ROUND TWO - SEPTEMBER 28th - OCTOBER 20TH  The SynchroLife Team has decided to offer a second round of bounty to help spread the word and deepen understanding about the SynchroLife project. Fans and supporters of SynchroLife can earn SynchroCoin for spreading the news! These bounties include Twitter and Facebook bounties, SynchroLife app bounties, translation bounties, and blog/article bounties.  The first round bounty campaign ended as of September 27th, 2017. All participants of the first bounty campaign will receive their SynchroCoin tokens for that participation after the end of the SynchroLife crowdsale (after October 20th, 2017).  You can see the details of the first round of the bounty on our blog here: https://medium.com/@synchrocoin/synchrolife-token-crowdsale-bounty-1dbd63b8c4d4 You can see the details of the second round of bounty on our blog here: https://medium.com/@synchrocoin/synchrolife-crowdsale-bounty-campaign-round-2-september-27th-october-20th-e6fabce94760  Bounty Overview 1. Social Media: Daily Twitter or Facebook shares 2. Social Media: Download & Register for the SynchroLife app 3. Translation: Bitcointalk.org Announcement 4. Blog: Original blog post or article  If you have any questions regarding the bounties please contact the SynchroLife Team at info@synchrolife.org or leave a comment here We will do our best to reply to all messages and questions as soon as possible.  Without further ado, here are the SynchroLife bounty campaign details![/size]  ・・・・・    Daily Twitter and Facebook Bounty  Bounty: 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Twitter (1 stake per day per Twitter post) 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Facebook (1 stake per day per Facebook post)  Requirements: - Share or retweet a post from an official SynchroLife account (Facebook “SynchroCoin”, Twitter “@synchrocoin”) or make an original post which includes a link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) or our Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin. Please note that if your post is private, friends only, or locked we may not be able to verify it. - You must leave the share/retweet/post up until at least the end of the bounty campaign period (October 20, 2017). If the share is no longer avaliable when we check it will not be counted. - Only ONE Facebook post and ONE Twitter post per user per day. Attempts to make multiple accounts or count posts in one day for the whole month will be disqualified and immediately blacklisted from all bounties when discovered. - Twitter accounts must have more than 50 followers. Facebook accounts must have more than 50 friends. - You must follow our official Twitter account to be counted for the Twitter bounty. Similarly, you must like the official Facebook page to be counted for the Facebook bounty.  Please note this is a daily bounty. This means once a day. 😊  🐦 How to Apply for Twitter:  1. Follow SynchroLife on Twitter (@synchrocoin, http://www.twitter.com/synchrocoin) 2. Retweet a Tweet by the official account OR make your own original Tweet that links to the official crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) OR make your own original Tweet that links to our official Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin) 3. Once you have tweeted, fill out this form to apply for the bounty: https://goo.gl/forms/XDaH27cRUuON0ahA3 You can apply for the Twitter bounty once a day. You can fill out the Google Form daily, weekly, or all at the end of the campaign, however is easiest for you. Please note the Google Form requires you to link to the Tweets that you retweeted or to your original Tweets so they can be counted. See the details of the form here: https://goo.gl/forms/XDaH27cRUuON0ahA3  All participants will get 1 stake per retweet or original tweet, up to once a day.  👤 How to Apply for Facebook:  1. Like the official SynchroLife crowdsale Facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/synchrocoin)Post a link to the SynchroLife token crowdsale website (http://synchrolife.org) on your Facebook account 2. Share a Facebook post by the official account OR make your own original Facebook post that links to the official crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) OR make your own original Facebook post that links to our official Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin) 3. Once you have shared or posted, fill out this form to apply for the bounty: https://goo.gl/forms/w9OlxfI63A2WBqbY2 You can apply for the Facebook bounty once a day. You can fill out the Google Form daily, weekly, or all at the end of the campaign, however is easiest for you. Please note the Google Form requires you to link to the Facebook posts that you shared or to your original Facebook posts so they can be counted. See the details of the form here: https://goo.gl/forms/w9OlxfI63A2WBqbY2  All participants will get 1 stake per Facebook post share or original Facebook post, up to once a day.  ・・・・・    Register for the SynchroLife iOS or Android App * One per participant  Bounty: 30 SynchroCoin (SYC) for registering  Requirements: - You must download the SynchroLife app for either iOS (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449) or Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife) and register for an account. Downloading the app and registering for the app is completely free. - Only ONE account per person, even if you have multiple phones. Attempts to make multiple fake accounts will be disqualified and immediately blacklisted from all bounties when discovered. - You must notify the SynchroLife Team after you have registered so we can verify your account!. Please fill out this Google Form once you have registered for SynchroLife: https://goo.gl/forms/ppj985mI4mb88fpO2  📲 iOS (iPhone) App Store Download Link: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449 📲 Android Google Play Download Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife You can also search “SynchroLife” in your respective official app store to download.  How to Apply: 1. Download the SynchroLife app for iOS (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449) or Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife). 2. Register for an account with SynchroLife. You can register with email, Facebook, Twitter, or Google＋. All types of registration are acceptable for participating in this bounty. 3. Follow the instructions within the app to complete your registration. Pick your country and favorite food and once you get to the HOME screen your registration is complete! 4. After you have finished registering, fill out this Google Form https://goo.gl/forms/ppj985mI4mb88fpO2 with your SynchroLife account name, the email you have assigned to your SynchroLife account, and your Ether address where you would like to receive the SynchroCoin bounty payment. 5. We will verify if your account is registered for SynchroLife, and if it is you will receive the bounty! If we have any issues verifying your account we will attempt to contact you via the email you have registered with your SynchroLife account.  ・・・・・    BitcoinTalk Announcement Translation  Bounty: 2500 SynchroCoin (SYC) for translation  Our current Bitcointalk announcement can be viewed here: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2006207.0  Requirements: - Rank “Junior Member” or above only - User must be willing to post the translation on the coordinating language forum on Bitcointalk.org - Natural translations only, no machine translations (i.e. Google Translate). We will check and and may reject suspicious translations. - You must translate the main text. Images are not required. - Translation must ideally be finished by October 4th or sooner. - Apply via this Google Form and we will contact you via Bitcointalk direct message: https://goo.gl/forms/aoN7Xh4N9DgVffvx2  Languages We Are Accepting: Bahasa Indonesia (Indonesian) (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)、Hrvatski (Croatian)、Deutsch (German)、Eλληνικά (Greek) (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)、עברית (Hebrew)、Français (French)、Italiano (Italian) (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)、Nederlands (Dutch)、Philippines (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)、Polski (Polish)、Português (Portuguese)、Pyccкий (Russian) (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)、Română (Romanian)、Skandinavisk、Türkçe (Turkish) (Currently waiting for confirmation from applicant)  Languages We Are No Longer Accepting: English, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Spanish, Hindi  How to Apply: Please fill out this Google Form https://goo.gl/forms/aoN7Xh4N9DgVffvx2 with your BitcoinTalk username, a link to your Bitcointalk profile, and examples any previous translation experience (cryptocurrency/crowdsale related or otherwise). We will contact you via Bitcointalk direct message if we decide to accept your application. We will give preference based on experience as well as order in which we received a proposal. Do not start translating until you receive approval.  We have received offers for some translations before the announcement of this second bounty. Those translators will be contacted and given 48 hours to decided if they still want to do the new translation bounty before we offer those languages to other translators. Thank you for your understanding.  ・・・・・    Blog and Website Article Post Bounty * Accepting up to 30 articles  Bounty: 450 SynchroCoin (SYC) for one blog post or article  Requirements: - Must an original and unique blog post or article introducing the SynchroLife service and crowdsale. Copy pasting (for example, copy and pasting from our press release, white paper, website, Bitcointalk announcement, other news sites, etc) the entire article will not be accepted. If the SynchroLife team believes your post lacks originality we may ask you to rewrite it. - Blog or article post may be in any language. - Must be 500 words in English (or rough equivalent in your language) - Blog must contain at least one link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (http://synchrolife.org) and to the iOS App Store (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449) and Google Play (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife) pages for SynchroLife. - All images or other content used in the article must be copyright free or owned by you. We can provide any images of SynchroLife as needed including screenshots, images from the website, images from the white paper, and food/restaurant images if needed. You can start with the images here: https://www.dropbox.com/sh/r0j2xfca95q01d7/AAA_MXa1mNlIEXgx3oxin1gsa?dl=0 - Websites and blogs related to cryptocurrency, technology, startups, mobile apps, or food are preferred. - Articles will be approved in the order they are received, up to a maximum of 50 articles.  How to Apply: 1. Write your article and post it on your blog or website 2. Contact the SynchroLife Team by filling out this Google Form with a link to your article and other information: https://goo.gl/forms/RsbQUcjhERNfApK63 3. The SynchroLife Team will check your article for originality. If approved, we will contact you by email as soon as possible with a code to add to you article. 4. Update your article with the code you received and your article bounty will be accepted.  ・・・・・   Thank you for your interest in SynchroLife and the SynchroLife Bounty Campaign!  Again, if you have any questions regarding the bounties please contact the SynchroLife Team at info@synchrolife.org or contact us via Twitter or Slack. We will do our best to reply to all messages and questions as soon as possible.  Have a nice day, hope to see you all in the SynchroLife community! 😊  * The details of the first round of the SynchroLife Bounty Campaign can be read on our official Medium blog here: https://medium.com/@synchrocoin/synchrolife-token-crowdsale-bounty-1dbd63b8c4d4  * Please Note: SynchroLife Limited reserves the right to restrict tokens to individual users. Rules and regulations of bounty are subject to change. All changes to the bounty campaign will be notified here in the SynchroLife Bounty Campaign Bitcointalk.org thread as well as in the official Medium blog post  as soon as possible.  * All of this information is also in the first post on this bounty thread. We are also posting it as a comment to make it clear the second round of the bounty was announced today, September 28th 2017.

Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Over the past week we have received multiple blog bounty submissions that were claiming plagiarized articles copied from cryptocurrency news sites and other blogs as their own by reposting the articles on Medium accounts.  We check ALL blog bounty submissions for originality and uniqueness before approving them for bounty. All plagiarized or otherwise copied articles will be immediately rejected.  It has been in our bounty rules since day one that for the blog/article bounty you must write a unique and original article. We also believe it is common sense that you should NEVER be copy and pasting someone else's new article or blog post and claiming it as your own. Thanks for your understanding  If you are a blog/article bounty participant and notice you article being reposted or copied without your permission please let us know and we will make sure we have blacklisted that entry. We are doing our best to carefully check every application.

We still have bounty open for Twitter, Facebook, "invite a friend" to SynchroLife, blog/article bounty, and video bounty! Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Sure, here are the instructions for the blog/article campaign!  7. Blog and Website Article Post Bounty  Bounty: 450 SynchroCoin (SYC) for one blog post or article  Requirements: - Must an original and unique blog post or article introducing the SynchroLife service and crowdsale. Copy pasting (for example, copy and pasting from our press release, white paper, website, Bitcointalk announcement, other news sites, etc) the entire article will not be accepted. If the SynchroLife team believes your post lacks originality we may ask you to rewrite it. - Blog or article post may be in any language. - Must be 500 words in English (or rough equivalent in your language) - Blog must contain at least one link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (http://synchrolife.org) and to the iOS App Store (https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449) and Google Play (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife) pages for SynchroLife. - All images or other content used in the article must be copyright free or owned by you. We can provide any images of SynchroLife as needed including screenshots, images from the website, images from the white paper, and food/restaurant images if needed. - Websites and blogs related to cryptocurrency, technology, startups, mobile apps, or food are preferred. - Articles will be approved in the order they are received, up to a maximum of 50 articles.  How to Apply: 1. Write your article and post it on your blog or website 2. Contact the SynchroLife Team by filling out this Google Form with a link to your article and other information: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfzG5TGOfTJEqJXDeDpoiJQ7y_-c8X0vUVbpjfmfdBmRN2h9g/viewform?usp=sf_link 3. The SynchroLife Team will check your article for originality. If approved, we will contact you by email within 72 hours with a code to add to you article. 3. Update your article with the code you received and your article bounty will be accepted.

Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello everyone, thank you for your interest in SynchroLife! I just wanted to address a couple points that are coming up a lot. I will also be replying to messages received both on this thread and directly as soon as possible to answer any questions. Thank you for your understanding!  Update Regarding Translation Bounty  We have received many translation requests, thank you for your interest! We have currently closed all translation bounties and are currently contacting all translators who emailed us regarding participating, and decided on positions now. If any positions end up unfilled or open up again we will be sure to notify the community and other applicants as soon as possible.  Update Regarding Payment  There have been multiple questions about when bounty participants will receive their SynchroCoin token bounty. SynchroLife is preparing for a token crowdsale, currently scheduled for August 3, 2017 to September 3, 2017. All SynchroCoin bounty payments will be made after the end of the SynchroCoin token crowdsale, when all tokens are distributed. Check the SynchroLife website and official social media and tuned for more information about when you will receive your SynchroCoin tokens!  This applies to the tokens for all bounties (social, translation, signature, blog, etc).  Update Regarding Social Media Shares  There have been several questions regarding the social media bounty and how many times one person can participate. Please read the original post for all details, but in general it is only ONE Facebook post and ONE Twitter post per user. Of course you are welcome to share more than that and we would love if you did but we will only be paying bounty for one post per user. There is no retweet or "likes" bounty. This has been in the bounty description both here on Bitcointalk and on our Medium blog since the beginning of the bounty, we apologize if there has been any confusion.  We may offer more social media bounties in the future, so stay tuned!

Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello, thank you for your interest in SynchroLife!  Like any team, of course we cannot guarantee 100% that we will keep to an exact timeline, but just like our supporters and participants in the upcoming crowdsale of course we want to move alone the road map as quickly as possible to allow the token economy in the service to properly grow! We have been working on SynchroLife for several years and are dedicated to making the platform a success.  Our team is active now and we are continuously updating the current app. For reference, our last update for the Android app was this past Wednesday, July 12th as you can see in Google Play (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife), and our most recent iOS update was July 6th (https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id557532449?mt=8). Our server engineer is working on some bugs this Friday evening as we speak  We still have a lot of work to do improving the current app, and we are excited to start development to move the platform's restaurant database to the blockchain and to incorporate the SynchroCoin tokens as soon as possible this upcoming fall and winter. We already have a user base of over 30,000 users and we want to bring them the best service possible ASAP.  Here is our road map from our white paper for your reference:  August 3, 2017 – September 3, 2017 SynchroCoin Token Crowdsale   January – March 2018 Release of the decentralized restaurant recommendation platform. Including: - SynchroCoin token usability within the app - Synchro Wallet within the app (available to hold Bitcoin, Ethereum, and SynchroCoin) - The start of a monthly subscription based premium membership service   June – August 2018 “Participating Restaurant” services released. A new mobile app and website just for restaurant managers, including: - Ability to create and publish digital coupons and gift cards - Ability to mark when users come to their restaurant - Ability to buy SynchroCoin tokens - Ability to offer bonus SynchroCoin tokens as rewards   November 2018 – January 2019 Release full customer relation management (CRM) tool suite for participating restaurants   January – March 2019 Release cryptocurrency payment service for participating restaurants, including: - Ability to exchange cryptocurrenies - Ability for restaurants to process payments in the participating restaurant app   March – April 2019 Release of the “Synchro” debit card (allowing users to make purchases with Bitcoin, Ethereum, or SynchroCoin).   And here's some pictures from offline meetups we have done with users of the beta version of SynchroLife in Japan, just in case you were curious about our team and beta community! Summer BBQ Party - https://www.facebook.com/synchrolife.jp/posts/687906001352748 Dinner Party in Tokyo - https://www.facebook.com/synchrolife.jp/posts/783552651788082 Dinner Party in Osaka - https://www.facebook.com/synchrolife.jp/posts/651845774958771   I hope that helped to answer some of your questions and give you a clearer idea about our project road map and development. Let me know if you have any other questions, and have a nice weekend

Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: SYNCHROLIFE BOUNTY CAMPAIGN Welcome to the Official SynchroLife Bounty Campaign Thread! Last updated October 25, 2018    SynchroLife is the world’s first blockchain based restaurant recommendation platform, providing trustworthy restaurant information and reviews worldwide by rewarding reviewers with tokens.  BOUNTY IS NOW OVER ALL TOKENS DISTRIBUTED  _______________________________________________________________  OFFICAL WEBSITE｜WHITE PAPER｜BLOG｜TOKEN CALCULATION _______________________________________________________________  TWITTER｜FACEBOOK｜TELEGRAM｜REDDIT｜GITHUB｜iOS iPHONE APP｜ANDROID APP _______________________________________________________________  ENGLISH ANN｜KOREAN ANN｜CHINESE ANN｜SPANISH ANN _______________________________________________________________    The SynchroLife Team has decided to offer a second round of bounty to help spread the word and deepen understanding about the SynchroLife project. Fans and supporters of SynchroLife can earn SynchroCoin for spreading the news! These bounties include Twitter and Facebook bounties, SynchroLife app bounties, translation bounties, and blog/article bounties.  The first round bounty campaign ended as of September 27th, 2017. All participants of the first bounty campaign will receive their SynchroCoin tokens for that participation after the end of the SynchroLife crowdsale (after October 20th, 2017).  You can see the details of the first round of the bounty on our blog here: https://medium.com/@synchrocoin/synchrolife-token-crowdsale-bounty-1dbd63b8c4d4 You can see the details of the second round of bounty on our blog here: https://medium.com/@synchrocoin/synchrolife-crowdsale-bounty-campaign-round-2-september-27th-october-20th-e6fabce94760  New to SynchroLife? Learn more about SynchroLife and our token crowdsale at the links below! Official Site: http://synchrolife.org White paper: http://synchrolife.org/whitepaper.html Bitcointalk.org ANN Thread: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2006207.0 Twitter: http://twitter.com/synchrocoin Facebook: http://facebook.com/synchrocoin iPhone App — iOS App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id557532449 Android App — Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.synchrolife  Bounty Overview 1. Social Media: Daily Twitter or Facebook shares 2. Social Media: Download & Register for the SynchroLife app 3. Translation: Bitcointalk.org Announcement 4. Blog: Original blog post or article  What is a “bounty” or “bounty campaign”? A bounty campaign is a PR event where supporters and fans of a project help to spread the news, increase awareness, and generally assist in publicizing the project. These campaigns are frequently used by token crowdsale projects. Supports and fans can join earn tokens for their participation. SynchroLife is offering 1% of SynchroCoin tokens (1,000,000) for this bounty campaign.  Regarding SynchroCoin Payment All SynchroCoin bounty payments will be made after the end of the SynchroCoin token crowdsale. The crowdsale is currently scheduled to end on October 20, 2017. Check the SynchroLife website and official social media and tuned for more information about when you will receive your SynchroCoin tokens!  Regarding the value of 1 SynchroCoin Token The SynchroLife token crowdsale does not have a preset price for the value of one SynchroCoin (SYC) token. The total sold 55,000,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst token crowdsale participants based on the amount of ETH each individual participant contributed during the token crowdsale (including any relevant bonuses) and the total amount raised during the crowdsale.  Please see our blog for more information and examples on how the price of SynchroCoin tokens will be calculated and how they will be distributed to participants of the SynchroLife token crowdsale.  If you have any questions regarding the bounties please contact the SynchroLife Team at info@synchrolife.org or leave a comment here We will do our best to reply to all messages and questions as soon as possible.  Without further ado, here are the SynchroLife bounty campaign details!  ・・・・・    Daily Twitter and Facebook Bounty  Bounty: 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Twitter (1 stake per day per Twitter post) 150,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be distributed amongst participants for Facebook (1 stake per day per Facebook post)  Requirements: - Share or retweet a post from an official SynchroLife account (Facebook “SynchroCoin”, Twitter “@synchrocoin”) or make an original post which includes a link to the SynchroLife crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) or our Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin. Please note that if your post is private, friends only, or locked we may not be able to verify it. - You must leave the share/retweet/post up until at least the end of the bounty campaign period (October 20, 2017). If the share is no longer avaliable when we check it will not be counted. - Only ONE Facebook post and ONE Twitter post per user per day. Attempts to make multiple accounts or count posts in one day for the whole month will be disqualified and immediately blacklisted from all bounties when discovered. - Twitter accounts must have more than 50 followers. Facebook accounts must have more than 50 friends. - You must follow our official Twitter account to be counted for the Twitter bounty. Similarly, you must like the official Facebook page to be counted for the Facebook bounty.  Please note this is a daily bounty. This means once a day. 😊  🐦 How to Apply for Twitter:  1. Follow SynchroLife on Twitter (@synchrocoin, http://www.twitter.com/synchrocoin) 2. Retweet a Tweet by the official account OR make your own original Tweet that links to the official crowdsale website (https://synchrolife.org) OR make your own original Tweet that links to our official Medium blog (https://medium.com/@synchrocoin) 3. Author: synchrocoin
Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello, thank you for your interest in SynchroLife!  For the Facebook county campaign you only need to make one post. Currently it is a one post per person, one time system. Make one post on your Facebook account with a link to the SynchroLife crowdsale site (https://synchrolife.org/), and then send us a Facebook message at our Facebook page (https://www.facebook.com/synchrocoin) with a link to your post and the ETH address at with you would like to receive your SynchroCoin tokens.  So the order is: 1. Make a post on your Facebook account with a link to the SynchroLife crowdsale site (for example: "Check out SynchroLife, the world's first blockchain based restaurant recommendation platform! https://synchrolife.org/"). 2. Send a private Facebook message to our page (https://www.facebook.com/synchrocoin) from your account (so we know it's you!) with a link to your post and the ETH address at with you would like to receive your SynchroCoin tokens.  I hope that is easier to understand, let me know if you're still confused!

Title: SynchroLife: Steemit for restaurant reviews [BOUNTY ENDED 10/20]
Body: Hello! Thank you for your interest in SynchroLife, I'm sorry we weren't clear about the pool! I added a bit to the bounty post and I will also share that here.  Regarding the Pool Size: Of the total 100,000,000 SynchroCoin tokens, 1% will be used for bounty. So a total of up to 1,000,000 SynchroCoin tokens will be used for bounty. Unused bounty tokens will be moved to the SynchroLife business pool (9,500,000 (9.5%)) and used for other efforts to grow the platform.  Regarding the price of the token: The exact details of SynchroLife’s SynchroCoin token crowdsale will be announced soon, however during the crowdsale 55,000,000 tokens will be sold. If our crowdsale raises $10,000,000, 1 SynchroCoin will be worth approximately $0.18 (USD). Please understand the exact value amount will change based on the total funds raised during the crowdsale. We cannot guarantee the value of 1 SynchroCoin.  The crowdsale starts August 3, 2017 at 12:00 noon GMT   For more details regarding the SynchroCoin and the SynchroLife token crowdsale, please refer to our official website (http://synchrolife.org) and white paper (http://synchrolife.org/whitepaper.html).
